data.description: Upon entering the house, you will see a bright living room with beautifully finished hardwood floors that lead up to the kitchen. The kitchen has a breakfast bar and ample cabinet space. The highlight sought after open layout from the kitchen to the living room is ideal for entertaining friends and family. Upstairs there are 3 bedrooms including the master suite which has its own private 3/4 bathroom with custom tile. The full bathroom is conveniently located right outside the other two bedrooms. Downstairs is a spacious family room. This large room works great for both a bedroom, game room, office, or family room. There is a 3/4 bathroom located downstairs as well. The unfinished basement provides room for extra storage. The backyard is fully fenced and perfect for spending summer evenings out on the patio. The home is a must see!
